title: RareWare 3DBDBuster 4.5 [deepstatus]
description:
RareWare 3DBDBuster 4.5 [deepstatus]

+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| 3DBDBuster converts 3D Blu-ray titles to MKV/TS. It takes SSIF files as input|
| and allows you to convert to MKV/TS, with support for many types of          |
| 3D formats, including side-by-side, over/under,                              |
| and at various resolutions/bitrate.                                          |
|                                                                              |
| It also supports output to the openKMQ format.                               |
|                                                                              |
| Split SSIF files are also supported.                                         |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                              |
|                               1. Unpack                                      |
|                               2. Install                                     |
|                                                                              |
|        Attention, the  build-in codecs in this setup are outdated,           |
|                      please use current versions !                           |
|                                                                              |
|                               3. Use KeyFileMaker                            |
|                       (save Key.data to install directory)                   |
|                                                                              |
|                               4. Use it for some 3d Bluray rips :D           |
+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Notes: The Development was stopped and you can buy it nowhere                |
